            <div type="question">
                <p>Describe your hobbies.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 30 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I don't know if I prefere to draw or to cook. Drawing, because when I was a little girl, I used to draw everything I saw, everytime. And people told me I was an artist. But now, I don't draw anymore because I think that I don't have this &quot;mind child&quot; I had. I'm more intrested by food and health. One day, I want to be vegan, so I love cooking healthy meal, with organic food. It make me feel so good in my body and in my mind.</p>
            </div>
